---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Who I am and what I write about here."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-07-07')}
	aiUsage="assisted"
>
	<p>I'm Asif. I help people and solve problems.</p>

	<p>
		Fifteen-plus years, all over the stack: frontend, backend, emails, infra,
		data, mobile. Backend engineer at heart.
	</p>

	<p>
		Right now I build software with AI at a venture firm. Mostly CRM, agents,
		internal tools, and plumbing. I'm the only engineer here, so the work is a
		mix of building, fixing, writing things down, and trying not to
		overcomplicate it.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is where some of that spills out. Notes from shipping. Mistakes
		that turned into rules. Open-weight model stuff I'm tracking too closely.
		Sometimes family stuff. Dad of three, so that part sets more of the schedule
		than anything in my calendar.
	</p>

	<p>
		And if you go in for the old four humors: mostly fire, a little earth.
		Choleric with a melancholic streak. Sounds about right.
	</p>
</Layout>
